article_title: Female Physicians And The Future Of Healthcare Delivery

article_metadata.description: According to a recent Physicians Foundation survey, female physicians are more optimistic than their male counterparts about the future of medicine. This article explores the potential implications of this finding and examines the growing proportion of female physicians in the physician workforce.
article_metadata.author: Walker Ray, MD and Tim Norbeck
